parameters: Ameria readied her weapon and took a defensive stance.

\n<Roselitte>"...Relax. We are the Imperial Army. We've come to rescue
you."
\n<Yuri>"Leave this man to me. It's woman to woman, stay with her."

Before she could finish, Ameria threw herself into
Roselitte's chest.

\n<Ameria>"Sob... hic... I was so scared... I thought I was done
for... that I'd be sold off somewhere unknown..."

\n<Roselitte>"I see... But it's all right now. This place has been
secured by the Imperial Army. I guarantee your safety."
\n<Roselitte>"My name is Roselitte Schwarz... What's your name?"
Ameria stepped back from Roselitte in a flustered manner.

\n<Ameria>"I serve as a Sister at this church! Um, about earlier! Oh
my gosh...!"

\n<Roselitte>"Nice to meet you, Ameria. There's no need to be so formal.
You're not a soldier, after all."

\n<Ameria>"Um... I'm Ameria. Ameria Aulcrux. Thank you so much for
saving me. I don't know how to thank you enough."

\n<Roselitte>"Don't worry about it. I came here on my own accord. If you
want to thank someone, thank His Highness who led the troops
himself, and the soldiers outside."

\n<Ameria>"His Highness...? Oh, now that you mention it, earlier... Oh
my! Why would His Highness come all the way here? I must
greet him properly!"
\n<Ameria>"To be saved by Roselitte-sama... I'm so... so happy!"
\n<Ameria>"This must be God's will. Thank you, God! Hallelujah!"

\n<Ameria>"Ah, um... Hallelujah. It's a word we use to express our
thanks to God."

\n<Ameria>"When we're happy or joyful... when we want to express our
gratitude. That's when we use it."

\n<Roselitte>"...So, you're not injured, are you? Let's get out of here
for now."
\n<Ameria>"Ah, yes! Thank you so much, Roselitte-sama."
